---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Angel Barbosa · Full-Stack Developer (Go, Flutter, React, OCI)"
  description="Portfolio of Angel Ezequiel Barbosa Lomeli. I take complete systems from idea to production."
>
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24">
    <p data-boot class="font-mono text-label font-medium tracking-wide text-accent uppercase">
      <span
        class="mr-1.5 inline-block size-2 rounded-full bg-accent align-middle"
        aria-hidden="true"></span>
      in production · v2026.07
    </p>
    <h1 data-boot class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-display">
      I take complete systems from idea to production.
    </h1>
    <p data-boot class="mt-4 font-mono text-ink-soft">Go · Flutter · React · Cloud (OCI)</p>
    <p data-boot class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-ink-soft">
      Redesign bootstrap (phase 1): stack, tokens, theme and language. The real content (hero, ACP
      Suite case study, projects and certifications) lands in the next phases.
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>
